<text id="99" date="2011-01-18" length="short" lengthw="180" duration="short" durations="89.0" speed="slow" speedwm="121.3" delivery="read" topic="Health" topicspec="Patients' rights in cross border healthcare" type="Italian spoken sources" comments="NA">
<speaker name="Rossi Oreste" gender="M" country="Italy" politfunc="MEP" politgroup="EFD">
<st language="it" length="short" lengthw="181" duration="short" durations="89.0" speed="slow" speedwm="122.0" delivery="read">
<interpreter id="NA" gender="NA" native="NA">
<s id="99:1" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=99&start=00.06&end=00.09&collection=eptic3">
Onorevoli colleghi , inizialmente la direttiva presentava punti critici .
</s>
<s id="99:2" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=99&start=00.09&end=00.30&collection=eptic3">
In sede di discussione in commissione e in trilogo si è raggiunto un accordo su un testo nel complesso equilibrato , che tiene conto delle esigenze di qualità e sicurezza dell' assistenza sanitaria , dei principi generali dei rimborsi , dell' autorizzazione preventiva , della cooperazione transfrontaliera per la cura delle malattie rare e dei servizi di sanità elettronica .
</s>
<s id="99:3" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=99&start=00.30&end=00.40&collection=eptic3">
L' obiettivo che si è cercato di raggiungere è di riconoscere a tutti i pazienti il diritto all' assistenza sanitaria transfrontaliera , scongiurando il turismo sanitario .
</s>
<s id="99:4" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=99&start=00.40&end=00.51&collection=eptic3">
Le spese che vengono sostenute dal servizio sanitario per curare un cittadino di un altro paese membro devono , giustamente , essere a carico dello Stato di origine del paziente .
</s>
<s id="99:5" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=99&start=00.51&end=01.01&collection=eptic3">
Noi avremmo voluto altresì inserire l' obbligo per i paesi membri di garantire dei livelli essenziali di assistenza sanitaria , ma non è stato possibile .
</s>
<s id="99:6" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=99&start=01.01&end=01.24&collection=eptic3">
Il nostro voto , visto il lavoro di mediazione migliorativo del testo , sarà a favore , come lo sarà anche sull' altro testo in discussione riguardante l' iniziativa europea sulla malattia di Alzheimer e le altre forme di demenza... testo propedeutico alla presentazione di una proposta legislativa volta a creare un' integrazione tra le diverse politiche esistenti .
</s>
<s id="99:7" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=99&start=01.24&end=01.34&collection=eptic3">
L' obiettivo comune di tutti e 2 i provvedimenti è di sottolineare l' esigenza di un miglior coordinamento fra gli Stati membri nell' interesse esclusivo dei cittadini .
</s>
</interpreter>
</st>
</speaker>
</text>
<text id="98" date="2011-01-18" length="short" lengthw="200" duration="short" durations="96.0" speed="slow" speedwm="125.0" delivery="read" topic="Health" topicspec="Patients' rights in cross border healthcare" type="Italian spoken sources" comments="NA">
<speaker name="Ronzulli Licia" gender="F" country="Italy" politfunc="MEP" politgroup="PPE">
<st language="it" length="short" lengthw="199" duration="short" durations="96.0" speed="slow" speedwm="124.4" delivery="read">
<interpreter id="NA" gender="NA" native="NA">
<s id="98:1" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=98&start=00.07&end=00.23&collection=eptic3">
Sì , grazie Presidente , dopo un percorso giuridico durato anni , domani finalmente verrà votata la relazione che darà una base legislativa certa ai cittadini europei che ogni anno devono rivolgersi all' estero per ottenere cure mediche ed appropriate .
</s>
<s id="98:2" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=98&start=00.23&end=00.35&collection=eptic3">
Questo permetterà a tutti i pazienti , e non solo ai più informati o ai più fortunati , di beneficiare dei diritti che già sono riconosciuti negli anni nelle sentenze della Corte di giustizia dell' Unione europea .
</s>
<s id="98:3" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=98&start=00.35&end=00.53&collection=eptic3">
Attraverso l' apertura dei punti di contatto nazionali , accedere alla sanità transfrontaliera non sarà più un salto nel buio in cui , fino ad oggi , il paziente , già debilitato dalla malattia , ha dovuto purtroppo spesso affrontare problemi burocratici , linguistici ed economici .
</s>
<s id="98:4" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=98&start=00.53&end=01.08&collection=eptic3">
Per quanto riguarda le cure ospedaliere , lo Stato di affiliazione potrà richiedere al paziente che decide di farsi curare all' estero un' autorizzazione preventiva e questo è necessario ovviamente per tutelare la stabilità del proprio sistema... sanitario .
</s>
<s id="98:5" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=98&start=01.08&end=01.22&collection=eptic3">
Su alcuni punti si sarebbe forse potuto fare di più per tutelare i pazienti , come ad esempio per quanto riguarda il sistema di notifica preventiva che permetterà agli Stati membri di anticipare le spese mediche , ma solo su base volontaria .
</s>
<s id="98:6" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=98&start=01.22&end=01.42&collection=eptic3">
Infine , permettetemi di sottolineare quanto sia entusiasta di partecipare a un dibattito che , ehm assolutamente in modo trasversale , ha soltanto un comune denominatore , che è la priorità di porre fine al calvario di migliaia di pazienti in tutta Europa e finalmente questo momento sembra essere arrivato .
</s>
<s id="98:7" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=98&start=01.42&end=01.43&collection=eptic3">
Grazie .
</s>
</interpreter>
</st>
</speaker>
</text>
<text id="100" date="2011-01-18" length="short" lengthw="119" duration="short" durations="62.0" speed="slow" speedwm="115.2" delivery="read" topic="Health" topicspec="Patients' rights in cross border healthcare" type="Italian spoken sources" comments="NA">
<speaker name="Iacolino Salvatore" gender="M" country="Italy" politfunc="MEP" politgroup="PPE">
<st language="it" length="short" lengthw="118" duration="short" durations="62.0" speed="slow" speedwm="114.2" delivery="read">
<interpreter id="NA" gender="NA" native="NA">
<s id="100:1" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=100&start=00.05&end=00.17&collection=eptic3">
Grazie Presidente , questo provvedimento è sicuramente un provvedimento organico , per cui bisogna dare atto alla relatrice e a coloro i quali hanno contribuito alla loro definizione un plauso sincero .
</s>
<s id="100:2" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=100&start=00.17&end=00.29&collection=eptic3">
Cure transfrontaliere significa abbattere per l' appunto le frontiere e dare libertà di scelta al paziente , in stretta correlazione a quella libertà di movimento che caratterizza l' Unione europea ;
</s>
<s id="100:3" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=100&start=00.30&end=00.41&collection=eptic3">
una mobilità sanitaria che viene adesso riconosciuta , sia per le malattie rare che per le... malattie altamente specialistiche che richiedono per l' appunto una pronta risposta .
</s>
<s id="100:4" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=100&start=00.41&end=00.48&collection=eptic3">
La tempestività e l' appropriatezza della... prestazione consentono di affermare un diritto che è quello alla salute ;
</s>
<s id="100:5" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=100&start=00.48&end=01.05&collection=eptic3">
una sanità che diventa elettronica , che riduce la disparità... di trattamento dei cittadini in Unione europea e , perché no , questo provvedimento in prospettiva può essere la premessa per un accreditamento di tipo europeo , con la garanzie elevate di standard tecnologici e personali .
</s>
<s id="100:6" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=100&start=01.05&end=01.06&collection=eptic3">
Grazie .
</s>
</interpreter>
</st>
</speaker>
</text>
<text id="101" date="2011-01-18" length="short" lengthw="119" duration="short" durations="58.0" speed="slow" speedwm="123.1" delivery="read" topic="Health" topicspec="Patients' rights in cross border healthcare" type="Italian spoken sources" comments="NA">
<speaker name="Pirillo Mario" gender="M" country="Italy" politfunc="MEP" politgroup="SD">
<st language="it" length="short" lengthw="118" duration="short" durations="58.0" speed="slow" speedwm="122.1" delivery="read">
<interpreter id="NA" gender="NA" native="NA">
<s id="101:1" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=101&start=00.06&end=00.26&collection=eptic3">
Grazie Presidente , l' accesso alle cure transfrontaliere in Europa ha presentato finora diversi limiti legati ai lunghi tempi di attesa , ad un complesso sistema di rimborsi , nonché ad una difficile individuazione delle responsabilità dell' assistenza clinica successiva alle cure transfrontaliere .
</s>
<s id="101:2" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=101&start=00.26&end=00.41&collection=eptic3">
La direttiva che il Parlamento europeo si accinge a votare è un importante passo avanti perché chiarisce questi aspetti amministrativi e migliora la cooperazione tra gli Stati , rafforzando nPIPPERO anche gli standard di qualità e di sicurezza delle cure stesse .
</s>
<s id="101:3" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=101&start=00.42&end=00.55&collection=eptic3">
Con l' istituzione dei centri informativi nazionali il paziente potrà avere conoscenza delle cure mediche disponibili in un altro Stato dell' Unione , degli adempimenti da assolvere e delle procedure di reclamo e di ricorso .
</s>
<s id="101:4" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=101&start=00.55&end=01.05&collection=eptic3">
È questa una opportunità che si basa non più sulle possibilità economiche , ma su un vero e proprio diritto di scelta più consapevole .
</s>
<s id="101:5" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=101&start=01.05&end=01.05&collection=eptic3">
Grazie .
</s>
</interpreter>
</st>
</speaker>
</text>
<text id="102" date="2011-01-18" length="medium" lengthw="729" duration="long" durations="362.0" speed="slow" speedwm="120.8" delivery="mixed" topic="Health" topicspec="European initiative on Alzheimer's disease and other dementias Asthma inhalers" type="Italian spoken sources" comments="NA">
<speaker name="Mazzoni Erminia" gender="F" country="Italy" politfunc="MEP" politgroup="PPE">
<st language="it" length="medium" lengthw="673" duration="long" durations="362.0" speed="slow" speedwm="111.5" delivery="mixed">
<interpreter id="NA" gender="NA" native="NA">
<s id="102:1" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=102&start=00.07&end=00.28&collection=eptic3">
Presidente la ringrazio , devo dire che ehm condivido anch ' io le perplessità sulla logica dell' abbinamento di questa interrogazione con la precedente relazione , ehm ma l' importante per me è che oggi quest' Aula si occupi dellPIPPERO dell' argomento ehm che è contenuto nella interrogazione da me presentata a nome della commissione per le petizioni .
</s>
<s id="102:2" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=102&start=00.28&end=00.46&collection=eptic3">
Questa interrogazione solleva un caso di denegata giustizia nei confronti di una piccola impresa europea per l' inerzia purtroppo consumata dalla Commissione dal ' 97 ad oggi , così come ha sostenuto anche la commissione affari legali che è stata interpellata per un parere dalla commissione che io presiedo .
</s>
<s id="102:3" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=102&start=00.46&end=00.55&collection=eptic3">
La vicenda riguarda un apparecchio medico , nello specifico un inalatore per asmatici , brevettato nel ' 90 e immesso regolarmente sul mercato .
</s>
<s id="102:4" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=102&start=00.55&end=01.17&collection=eptic3">
Questo prodotto rientra nella disciplina dettata dalla direttiva novantaquaPIPPERO 93CEE , la quale prevede che la conformità alle prescrizioni sia oggetto di autocertificazione da parte del produttore e affida poi alle autorità nazionali un potere di controllo sulla regolarità , attraverso delle attività di monitoraggio e di controllo a campione .
</s>
<s id="102:5" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=102&start=01.17&end=01.43&collection=eptic3">
Il prodotto , diffuso con successo sul mercato per 6 anni , quindi fino al ' 96 , in assenza di specifiche contestazioni e di rilievi che non sono stati mai documentati nel corso di oltre 15 anni , viene sottoposto a controllo da parte dell' Autorità governativa dell' Alta Baviera che chiede all' agenzia di magdebPIPPERO ehm alla commissione del Magdeburgo di rivedere l' autorizzazione rilasciata a questa società .
</s>
<s id="102:6" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=102&start=01.44&end=02.20&collection=eptic3">
Nel dicembre dello stesso anno , ehm la ehm comPIPPERO la commissione , il ministro della Salute della Sassonia-Anhalt ehm procede a questa attività di controllo e conclude la procedura dichiarando la perfetta conformità del prodotto alle prescrizioni normative , sollevando tra l' altro , al termine di questa procedura , un dubbio sulla fondatezza della richiesta solPIPPERO ehm della richiesta formulata dall' Autorità governativa dell' Alta Baviera e invitando la stessa , nel caso di dovessero permanere i dubbi , ad avviare la procedura di salvaguardia prevista dalla direttiva citata .
</s>
<s id="102:7" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=102&start=02.20&end=02.43&collection=eptic3">
Ehm nel ehm corso dell' anno successivo ehm si susseguono una serie di attività ma non documentate , delle quali abbiamo notizia solo de relato , e si arriva poi nel ' 97 , improvvisamente , senza nessuna comunicazione fatta al produttore , a un provvedimento da parte del ministro della Salute federale di ritiro del prodotto dal mercato .
</s>
<s id="102:8" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=102&start=02.44&end=03.02&collection=eptic3">
La procedura ehm viene avviata ehm nel ehm alla fine del ' 97 dal ministero - la procedura ai sensi dell' articolo 8 della direttiva citata - ma va a finire su un binario morto , perché non si hanno notizie , non viene avviata la fase delle consultazioni con il produttore .
</s>
<s id="102:9" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=102&start=03.02&end=03.24&collection=eptic3">
E nel silenzio generale il produttore , nel 2003 , ritenendo ehm di poter attribuire a questo silenzio un significato di ehm evidente negazione di quei rilievi non chiariti formulati dalle autorità tedesche , reimmette sul mercato il prodotto nel nell' anno a metà del 2003 .
</s>
<s id="102:10" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=102&start=03.24&end=03.34&collection=eptic3">
Purtroppo nel 2005 , sempre senza una comunicazione , le autorità tedesche ehm emettono un nuovo provvedimento di ritiro dal mercato di questo prodotto .
</s>
<s id="102:11" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=102&start=03.34&end=03.45&collection=eptic3">
Da precisare che non risulta ancora oggi , nonostante le reiterate richieste , alcun elemento che porti a chiarire il perché di questo ritiro del prodotto .
</s>
<s id="102:12" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=102&start=03.45&end=04.05&collection=eptic3">
Quindi : mancata comunicazione , mancato accertamento , ehm nePIPPERO negazione di qualunque possibilità di legittimo contraddittorio per il produttore e ehm conseguenze gravi di carattere economico per lo stesso , perché da oltre 15 anni è in attesa di una risposta e il suo prodotto non può circolare sul mercato .
</s>
<s id="102:13" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=102&start=04.05&end=04.29&collection=eptic3">
Aggiungo anche che , nel corso dei 6 anni ehm di diffusione del protoPIPPERO prodotto - e su questo ci sono documenti che sono stati forniti anche alla Commissione - nei 6 anni di distribuzione del prodotto si sono annotati dei notevoli risparmi nella spesa pubblica della sanità per il ridotto costo del prodotto e dei positivi effetti per i malati sofferenti di asma .
</s>
<s id="102:14" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=102&start=04.29&end=04.38&collection=eptic3">
Nel 2008 , visti vani tutti i tentativi formulati con le altre autorità , il ehm signor Klein , il produttore , si rivolge alla commissione per le petizioni .
</s>
<s id="102:15" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=102&start=04.38&end=05.12&collection=eptic3">
La commissione avvia la procedura nel corso di questa legislatura e , considerato il lungo tempo ehm della vicenda contenuta nella petizione , ehm avvia anche una consultazione informale con il Commissario , chiedendo di accelerare i tempi di una risposta , perché la richiesta del petente è una richiesta che va nell' ordine di ehm riconfermare la ehm conformità del prodotto alla normativa europea o , in subordine , quanto meno di avere un provvedimento impugnabile davanti alla Corte che quindi gli consenta di avere giustizia .
</s>
<s id="102:16" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=102&start=05.13&end=05.22&collection=eptic3">
Tutto questo non è avvenuto e nel corso della discussione ehm in commissione petizioni la Commissione europea , purtroppo , ha eluso le domande ancora una volta .
</s>
<s id="102:17" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=102&start=05.23&end=05.53&collection=eptic3">
Ecco perché la commissione ha deciso all' unanimità di arrivare in Aula e di chiedere in Aula alla Commissione delle risposte chiare , perché questa vicenda , è innegabile , solleva dei gravi dubbi sulla ehm su una ehm violazione della Carta dei diritti fondamentali e non solo per l' inerzia della Commissione , ma anche , e soprattutto , per la impossibilità nella quale è posto il petente , il signor Klein , di adire un' autorità giudiziaria .
</s>
<s id="102:18" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=102&start=05.53&end=06.08&collection=eptic3">
Pone delle ehm la vicenda pone delle ehm delle evidenti degli evidenti dubbi sulla violazione delle regole del mercato e sulla tutela della piccola impresa , ecco perché insistiamo per avere , qui , delle risposte alle domande formulate nella interrogazione .
</s>
<s id="102:19" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=102&start=06.08&end=06.09&collection=eptic3">
Grazie Presidente .
</s>
</interpreter>
</st>
</speaker>
</text>
<text id="103" date="2011-01-18" length="short" lengthw="127" duration="short" durations="64.0" speed="slow" speedwm="119.1" delivery="read" topic="Health" topicspec="European initiative on Alzheimer's disease and other dementias Asthma inhalers" type="Italian spoken sources" comments="NA">
<speaker name="Bartolozzi Paolo" gender="M" country="Italy" politfunc="MEP" politgroup="PPE">
<st language="it" length="short" lengthw="125" duration="short" durations="64.0" speed="slow" speedwm="117.2" delivery="read">
<interpreter id="NA" gender="NA" native="NA">
<s id="103:1" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=103&start=00.05&end=00.15&collection=eptic3">
Signor Presidente , onorevoli colleghi , le malattie neurodegenerative , e tra queste appunto l' Alzheimer , rappresentano una priorità sanitaria per l' Unione europea .
</s>
<s id="103:2" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=103&start=00.16&end=00.21&collection=eptic3">
La malattia in questione ha pesanti risvolti , non solo sanitari , per chi la subisce .
</s>
<s id="103:3" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=103&start=00.22&end=00.29&collection=eptic3">
Ma elevati infatti sono i costi che devono essere sostenuti per le cure dirette e per quelle informali .
</s>
<s id="103:4" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=103&start=00.29&end=00.38&collection=eptic3">
Il morbo di Alzheimer , infatti , non riguarda solo le persone che ne sono colpite , ma coinvolge anche tutti coloro che si occupano dei malati stessi .
</s>
<s id="103:5" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=103&start=00.39&end=01.09&collection=eptic3">
Si rende perciò necessaria una risposta europea al problema , una coordinazione globale tra gli Stati membri , una sinergia di azioni concertate che riguardano soprattutto l' ambito scientifico e di ricerca e che si faccia carico del potenziamento della prevenzione e la diagnosi per il perfezionamento delle cure disponibili , anche innovative , nonché della diffusione delle informazioni fra gli Stati sui risultati raggiunti all' interno degli stessi , incrementando nei cittadini il livello di conoscenza della malattia .
</s>
</interpreter>
</st>
</speaker>
</text>
<text id="107" date="2011-01-18" length="medium" lengthw="624" duration="medium" durations="346.0" speed="slow" speedwm="108.2" delivery="mixed" topic="Economics and Finance" topicspec="Question Time" type="Italian spoken sources" comments="NA">
<speaker name="Tajani Antonio" gender="M" country="Italy" politfunc="European Commission" politgroup="NA">
<st language="it" length="medium" lengthw="609" duration="medium" durations="346.0" speed="slow" speedwm="105.6" delivery="mixed">
<interpreter id="NA" gender="NA" native="NA">
<s id="107:1" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=107&start=00.05&end=00.23&collection=eptic3">
Signor Presidente , onorevoli... parlamentari , l' industria europea ehm del turismo , come molti altri settori economici , deve fronteggiare la sfida sempre più forte della ehm globalizzazione .
</s>
<s id="107:2" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=107&start=00.23&end=00.36&collection=eptic3">
Si tratta di una sfida che la Commissione ha già... sottolineato e affrontato a più riprese , in modo particolare con la comunicazione " Una politica industriale nell' era della globalizzazione " .
</s>
<s id="107:3" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=107&start=00.36&end=01.04&collection=eptic3">
Inoltre , il 30 giugno dello scorso anno la Commissione ha adottato una comunicazione specifica sul turismo , che propone , in linea con il trattato di Lisbona e la nuova strategia Europa 2020 , un quadro politico consolidato per rafforzare la competitività del settore , con l' aspirazione di fare del turismo europeo una vera industria competitiva moderna , stabile e responsabile .
</s>
<s id="107:4" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=107&start=01.05&end=01.16&collection=eptic3">
La creazione di un contesto favorevole allo sviluppo delle medie , piccole e piccolissime imprese del settore turistico rappresenta il principio fondamentale di questo quadro consolidato .
</s>
<s id="107:5" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=107&start=01.16&end=01.54&collection=eptic3">
Per oPIPPERO raggiungere l' obiettivo abbiamo proposto 3 azioni concrete che puntano primo a stimolare la competitività del settore turistico all' interno della nostra Unione , secondo a promuovere lo sviluppo di un turismo di lunga durata , responsabile e di qualità , terzo consolidare l' immagine e la visibilità dell' Europa come un insieme di destinazioni turistiche di lunga durata e di qualità e , naturalmente , massimizzare il potenziale delle politiche e degli strumenti finanziari dell' Unione per sviluppare il ehm turismo .
</s>
<s id="107:6" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=107&start=01.54&end=02.09&collection=eptic3">
Le iniziative promosse dovrebbero conferire al settore gli strumenti per adattarsi alle sfide al cospetto delle quali si trovano i suoi attori , nonché per intraprendere uno sviluppo durevole in termini di competitività .
</s>
<s id="107:7" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=107&start=02.10&end=02.43&collection=eptic3">
Saranno certamente portate in fase di attuazione misure concrete per promuovere l' innovazione nel settore del turismo , migliorare la qualità dei servizi turistici e perfezionare le competenze professionali del personale , perché non possiamo più pensare al turismo come un ehm settore ehm a conduzione esclusivamente familiare , ma dobbiamo pensare ad anche ad una organizzazione turistica più moderna e più competitiva .
</s>
<s id="107:8" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=107&start=02.44&end=03.00&collection=eptic3">
Vi farò qualche esempio a proposito della ehm formazione delle competenze professionali : una " piattaforma TIC e turismo " per facilitare l' adattamento del settore turistico e delle imprese all' evoluzione del mercato delle nuove tecnologie dell' informazione e accrescere la loro competitività .
</s>
<s id="107:9" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=107&start=03.01&end=03.09&collection=eptic3">
Ehm sono tutte proposte inserite , idee inserite nel testo della comunicazione della Commissione , approvata dal...
</s>
<s id="107:10" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=107&start=03.10&end=03.17&collection=eptic3">
Consiglio e che stiamo dibattendo in Parlamento , il relatore è presente in Aula .
</s>
<s id="107:11" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=107&start=03.17&end=03.32&collection=eptic3">
La mobilitazione degli attori dell' industria per un migliore utilizzo dei diversi programmi dell' Unione , come Leonardo , o ancora il programma quadro per l' innovazione e la competitività , l' Erasmus per i giovani imprenditori , il Fondo sociale europeo ed altri programmi .
</s>
<s id="107:12" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=107&start=03.32&end=03.50&collection=eptic3">
Inoltre , una strategia per la promozione di un' offerta turistica diversificata e la creazione di un' osservazioPIPPERO di un osservatorio virtuale con supporto elettronico per il turismo europeo permetteranno di contribuire in uguale maniera alla creazione di un contesto favorevole per gli attori del settore .
</s>
<s id="107:13" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=107&start=03.51&end=03.59&collection=eptic3">
Peraltro , bisogna ricordare che le piccole e medie imprese possono beneficiare di altre iniziative trasversali per accedere ai finanziamenti .
</s>
<s id="107:14" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=107&start=03.59&end=04.21&collection=eptic3">
Faccio cito il caso di JEREMIE , ehm iniziativa congiunta della Commissione , del Fondo europeo degli investimenti e della Banca europea degli investimenti , che punta a migliorare l' accesso delle piccolissime , piccole e medie imprese ai finanziamenti , in particolare attraverso il canale del capitale di rischio , dei prestiti , delle garanzie , del microcredito e di altre forme di aiuti rimborsabili .
</s>
<s id="107:15" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=107&start=04.21&end=04.43&collection=eptic3">
Vorrei infine ricordare che per le piccole e medie imprese nel settore del turismo... beneficiano ehm a pieno titolo delle misure proposte nel quadro dello Small Business Act che mira a facilitare il contesto operativo proprio delle piccole e medie imprese e che il Parlamento riceverà il testo di ehm aggiornamento nel giro di poche settimane .
</s>
<s id="107:16" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=107&start=04.44&end=05.19&collection=eptic3">
Quindi , lo Small Business Act diventa anche uno strumento per tutelare le piccole e medie imprese nel settore del turismo , che rappresentano ehm una ehm straordinaria potenzialità per sviluppare un settore che conto di poter potenziare nel prossimo anno , ehm perché sono assolutamente convinto che un una politica europea , così come prevista dal trattato , possa rappresentare un valore aggiunto al lavoro che già egregiamente svolgono le regioni dell' Unione europea e gli Stati membri .
</s>
<s id="107:17" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=107&start=05.20&end=05.50&collection=eptic3">
Quindi , credo di poter rassicurare l' onorevole ehm parlamentare che ha sottoposto ehm l' interrogazione ehm per con l' impegno ehm della Commissione e mio personale affinché tutte le piccole e medie imprese del settore possano essere sostenute e possano essere agevolate nell' accedere ai agli strumenti economici comunitari , in un contesto di una strategia politica che punta a fare del turismo uno dei settori di politica economica e industriale cardine .
</s>
<s id="107:18" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=107&start=05.50&end=05.51&collection=eptic3">
Vi ringrazio .
</s>
</interpreter>
</st>
</speaker>
</text>
<text id="105" date="2011-01-18" length="short" lengthw="154" duration="short" durations="63.0" speed="medium" speedwm="146.7" delivery="mixed" topic="Economics and Finance" topicspec="Question Time" type="Italian spoken sources" comments="NA">
<speaker name="Fidanza Carlo" gender="M" country="Italy" politfunc="MEP" politgroup="PPE">
<st language="it" length="short" lengthw="148" duration="short" durations="63.0" speed="medium" speedwm="141.0" delivery="mixed">
<interpreter id="NA" gender="NA" native="NA">
<s id="105:1" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=105&start=00.05&end=00.06&collection=eptic3">
Adesso tocca a me .
</s>
<s id="105:2" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=105&start=00.06&end=00.08&collection=eptic3">
Grazie Presidente , mi scuso per il disguido .
</s>
<s id="105:3" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=105&start=00.08&end=00.21&collection=eptic3">
Voglio ringraziare il collega Balcytis per questa interrogazione che pone al centro del nostro dibattito argomenti che il Parlamento avrà modo di affrontare anche nei prossimi mesi con la relazione parlamentare di cui sono ehm responsabile .
</s>
<s id="105:4" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=105&start=00.21&end=00.38&collection=eptic3">
Dobbiamo innanzitutto dare atto al vicepresidente Tajani di aver dato un impulso molto forte alla nuova politica europea del turismo prevista dalle competenze del trattato di Lisbona , con la comunicazione del giugno scorso e con il relativo piano di implementazione presentato pochi ehm poche settimane fa .
</s>
<s id="105:5" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=105&start=00.39&end=00.50&collection=eptic3">
Questi 2 atti hanno al centro proprio l' attenzione per le piccole e medie imprese , per la competitività del settore , in particolar modo le tematiche relative all' innovazione e alla formazione .
</s>
<s id="105:6" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=105&start=00.50&end=01.06&collection=eptic3">
Sui finanziamenti noi dobbiamo agire su 2 linee : innanzitutto rendere conoscibili e maggiormente utilizzati i fondi già esistenti e in secondo luogo il Parlamento dovrà fare una grande battaglia per avere nelle prospettive , concludo Presidente , 2014 - 2020 delle linee di finanziamento specifiche per le politiche del turismo .
</s>
<s id="105:7" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=105&start=01.08&end=01.09&collection=eptic3">
Grazie .
</s>
</interpreter>
</st>
</speaker>
</text>
<text id="106" date="2011-01-18" length="medium" lengthw="664" duration="medium" durations="303.0" speed="medium" speedwm="131.5" delivery="impromptu" topic="Economics and Finance" topicspec="Question Time" type="Italian spoken sources" comments="NA">
<speaker name="Tajani Antonio" gender="M" country="Italy" politfunc="European Commission" politgroup="NA">
<st language="it" length="medium" lengthw="619" duration="medium" durations="303.0" speed="slow" speedwm="122.6" delivery="impromptu">
<interpreter id="NA" gender="NA" native="NA">
<s id="106:1" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=106&start=00.05&end=00.27&collection=eptic3">
Grazie onorevole Presidente , io voglio ringraziare l' onorevole ehm Balcytis perché mi dà la possibilità di intervenire su un tema che mi sta particolarmente a cuore fra quelli di cui sono responsabile come Commissario europeo , essendo il primo Commissario europeo al turismo , lo considero , insieme alla politica industriale e alla politica dello spazio , una priorità .
</s>
<s id="106:2" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=106&start=00.28&end=01.01&collection=eptic3">
Il tema chiave , però , per rispondere poi concretamente , al di là delle iniziative politiche che ho ehm cercato di attuare da quando sono diventato Commissario , è quello che ha posto l' onorevole Fidanza nel corso del suo intervento , perché non essendoci una competenza comunitaria di politica del turismo prima del trattato di Lisbona , nelle attuali prospettive finanziarie non ci sono i fondi necessari per contribuire ehm con un aiuto ehm comunitario alla a una forte azione turistica .
</s>
<s id="106:3" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=106&start=01.01&end=01.24&collection=eptic3">
Abbiamo dei programmi interessanti come Calipso , che in Spagna sono stati valorizzati con iniziative regionali che mi sembrano molto ehm positive , ma ehm se ho ben capito il messaggio che ha lanciato l' onorevole Fidanza , nella relazione che verrà presentata dal Parlamento ci sarà un sostegno perché nelle prossime prospettive finanziarie ci sia un incremento dei fondi destinati alla politica del turismo .
</s>
<s id="106:4" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=106&start=01.24&end=01.33&collection=eptic3">
Questo può essere inserito all' interno dell -... dell' 8o programma quadro oppure con linee di bilancio ad hoc .
</s>
<s id="106:5" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=106&start=01.33&end=01.42&collection=eptic3">
Però è importante che il Parlamento ponga il problema , perché è difficile dare delle risposte concrete se non ci sono gli strumenti economici .
</s>
<s id="106:6" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=106&start=01.42&end=01.48&collection=eptic3">
Detto questo , non significa che noi non ci ehm muoveremo in maniera molto ehm determinata .
</s>
<s id="106:7" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=106&start=01.48&end=02.09&collection=eptic3">
Ehm come lei sa , le iniziative adottate sono state tantissime , la presidenza belga ha organizzato un grande evento a Malta , la presidenza ungherese ha già annunciato che ehm organizzerà un grande evento - è stato tema di colloquio in occasione del primo incontro che abbiamo avuto a Budapest ehm qualche ehm giorno fa - ehm un grande evento dedicato proprio al turismo .
</s>
<s id="106:8" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=106&start=02.09&end=02.40&collection=eptic3">
Per quPIPPERO e sono ehm contento anche che l' onorevole Balcytis abbia sPIPPERO posto il problema del turismo nel Baltico : il turismo non è un problema che riguarda le economie soltanto dei paesi dell' area mediterranea - Spagna , Francia , ehm Italia , Grecia e Malta - è una ehm risorsa ehm importantissima per tutta l' Unione europea , compresa ehm compresi i paesi dell' Europa centrale , dell' Europa dell' Est , che hanno delle bellezze e delle potenzialità da poter ehm sviluppare .
</s>
<s id="106:9" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=106&start=02.40&end=03.10&collection=eptic3">
E a proposito dei paesi del Baltico , io credo che uno dei temi , che peraltro è affrontato nel testo che è stato approvato il 30 di giugno dello scorso anno , c ' è il rapporto con le nuove classi emergenti , con la nuova borghesia ehm della Federazione russa , dove ci sono milioni e milioni di cittadini che intendono ehm svolgere attività turistica , quindi ehm vogliono uscire dai confini del loro paese .
</s>
<s id="106:10" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=106&start=03.10&end=03.12&collection=eptic3">
Abbiamo un problema per quanto riguarda i visti .
</s>
<s id="106:11" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=106&start=03.12&end=03.47&collection=eptic3">
Lo stesso problema esiste con la Cina , io credo , e è volontà della Commissione europea e dei ministri del Turismo di ehm cercare di risolvere questo problema , sia per quanto riguarda questo potenziale di turismo russo che questo potenziale di turismo ehm cinese , ehm per accelerare e fare in modo che ehm sia più facile ehm ricevere nei nostri paesi , e i paesi baltici , essendo più vicini alla Federazione russa , possano beneficiare di una presenza turistica anche di ehm classe media emergente che può portare dei benefici all' economia dei paesi baltici .
</s>
<s id="106:12" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=106&start=03.47&end=04.15&collection=eptic3">
Ecco , questo è pienamente nel centro della nostra ehm attività a favore delle politiche ehm turistiche e mi rallegro anche del fatto che molti ministri dei differenti paesi - ho incontrato ehm qualche settimana fa ehm a Londra il nuovo ministro del Turismo... britannico - anche la Gran Bretagna è fortemente impegnata per sostenere la politica turistica della Unione europea , lo stesso la Francia .
</s>
<s id="106:13" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=106&start=04.15&end=04.21&collection=eptic3">
Insomma , sarebbe importante individuare alcune porte di ingresso , perché l' Europa deve rappresentare un valore aggiunto .
</s>
<s id="106:14" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=106&start=04.21&end=04.36&collection=eptic3">
Sono ben lieto che la Commissaria Vassiliou abbia ehm voluto inserire nel testo approvato oggi che riguarda lo sport i grandi eventi sportivi - penso alle Olimpiadi di Londra ehm prossime venture - come una grande opportunità per tutta l' Unione europea .
</s>
<s id="106:15" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=106&start=04.36&end=04.48&collection=eptic3">
Insomma , dobbiamo fare in modo che ogni paese dell' Unione possa rappresentare una porta da dove entrano turisti che non si fermano in quel paese ma , dopo aver visitato quel paese , possano andare a visitare altri paesi europei .
</s>
<s id="106:16" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=106&start=04.49&end=04.55&collection=eptic3">
Questa è l' azione aggiuntiva che può fare la Commissione europea e il sostegno del Parlamento per me è determinante .
</s>
<s id="106:17" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=106&start=04.55&end=05.07&collection=eptic3">
Vi ringrazio per ciò che potrete fare , anche in occasione del dibattito sulla politica del turismo , ma anche per in ogni dibattito che riguarderà i prossimi ehm le prossime attività di bilancio .
</s>
<s id="106:18" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=106&start=05.07&end=05.07&collection=eptic3">
Vi ringrazio .
</s>
</interpreter>
</st>
</speaker>
</text>
<text id="108" date="2011-01-18" length="short" lengthw="176" duration="short" durations="77.0" speed="medium" speedwm="137.1" delivery="read" topic="Politics" topicspec="Situation in Haiti one year after the earthquake humanitarian aid and reconstruction" type="Italian spoken sources" comments="NA">
<speaker name="Rinaldi Niccolò" gender="M" country="Italy" politfunc="MEP" politgroup="ALDE">
<st language="it" length="short" lengthw="169" duration="short" durations="77.0" speed="medium" speedwm="131.7" delivery="read">
<interpreter id="NA" gender="NA" native="NA">
<s id="108:1" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=108&start=00.05&end=00.23&collection=eptic3">
Grazie Presidente , signori Commissari , cari colleghi , è proprio vero , Haiti è un caso a parte , diverso , perché ehm quando si ricorda l' anniversario di una calamità lo si fa sempre per ehm ricordare le vittime , per imparare meglio la lezione , ma ad Haiti è diverso , perché non c ' è niente da ricordare , niente è ancora passato .
</s>
<s id="108:2" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=108&start=00.23&end=00.46&collection=eptic3">
Anziché dire 1 anno dal terremoto dobbiamo dire 1 anno di terremoto , terremoto sismico , poi terremoto del disordine degli aiuti , terremoto sanitario con il colera , terremoto della politica con elezioni poco trasparenti e probabilmente nel momento meno opportuno e terremoto per certi aspetti anche storico , adesso , con il ritorno da equivoco turista miliardario dell' ex dittatore .
</s>
<s id="108:3" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=108&start=00.46&end=01.05&collection=eptic3">
La Commissione lavora bene , molto bene , sono stato ad Haiti ehm lo scorso giugno con la commissione sviluppo e ne ho visto ho visto l' ottimo lavoro e la ringraziamo , ma occorre anche una maggiore tutela politica con un ruolo accresciuto della comunità internazionale che indichi obiettivi , scadenze e che gestisca direttamente parte della ricostruzione .
</s>
<s id="108:4" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=108&start=01.05&end=01.12&collection=eptic3">
Ma questo deve essere bilanciato con un maggior coinvolgimento della popolazione e delle ONG locali , spesso invece tagliati fuori .
</s>
<s id="108:5" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=108&start=01.13&end=01.22&collection=eptic3">
Meno ruolo per la politica nazionale e le istituzioni nazionali governative di Haiti , dunque , e più per un partenariato finora debole tra cittadini e comunità internazionale .
</s>
</interpreter>
</st>
</speaker>
</text>
<text id="151" date="2011-01-18" length="short" lengthw="371" duration="medium" durations="154.0" speed="medium" speedwm="144.5" delivery="read" topic="Environment" topicspec="Waste crisis in Campania" type="Italian spoken sources" comments="NA">
<speaker name="Bizzotto Mara" gender="F" country="Italy" politfunc="MEP" politgroup="EFD">
<st language="it" length="short" lengthw="371" duration="medium" durations="154.0" speed="medium" speedwm="144.5" delivery="read">
<interpreter id="NA" gender="NA" native="NA">
<s id="151:1" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=151&start=00.07&end=00.19&collection=eptic3">
Grazie Presidente , la situazione che la Campania e in particolare la città di Napoli vivono da anni ormai è universalmente purtroppo nota a tutto il mondo e l' Unione europea ha dovuto occuparsi più volte della questione .
</s>
<s id="151:2" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=151&start=00.19&end=00.38&collection=eptic3">
Di fronte a tale situazione ormai paradossale da terzo mondo , chiedo pertanto alla Commissione a quali conseguenze andrà incontro l' Italia dal punto di vista del diritto comunitario e quali sanzioni economiche eventualmente saranno comminate all' Italia , nel caso la crisi dei rifiuti in Campania non dovesse trovare una soluzione definitiva in breve tempo .
</s>
<s id="151:3" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=151&start=00.38&end=00.51&collection=eptic3">
Chiedo inoltre se la Commissione può fornire nel dettaglio i dati relativi ai fondi europei che sono stati finora gestiti dalla regione Campania per la creazione di un sistema integrato di raccolta e smaltimento dei rifiuti .
</s>
<s id="151:4" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=151&start=00.51&end=01.01&collection=eptic3">
Vede signor Commissario , solitamente quando si parla di emergenza si parla di situazioni drammatiche , estreme , che tuttavia trovano una soluzione in tempi ragionevoli .
</s>
<s id="151:5" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=151&start=01.01&end=01.07&collection=eptic3">
Quando una cosiddetta " emergenza " dura da più di 15 anni , evidentemente c ' è qualcosa che non funziona .
</s>
<s id="151:6" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=151&start=01.08&end=01.30&collection=eptic3">
Il governo italiano in questi anni ha cercato di fare il possibile per risolvere l' annosa questione del ciclo di raccolta e smaltimento dei rifiuti ma , evidentemente , se oggi le strade di Napoli sono invase da tonnellate e tonnellate di immondizia la colpa è principalmente da addebitare alle autorità locali campane e alla loro totale incapacità o mancanza di volontà di adoperarsi per trovare una soluzione .
</s>
<s id="151:7" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=151&start=01.31&end=01.44&collection=eptic3">
È chiaro e assolutamente fuori da ogni dubbio che le condizioni in cui versano Napoli e la Campania è dovuto alla latitanza che hanno caratterizzato per tanti anni comune , provincia e regione nella gPIPPERO nella gestione del ciclo dei rifiuti .
</s>
<s id="151:8" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=151&start=01.44&end=01.53&collection=eptic3">
Se non viene fatta a dovere la raccolta differenziata , primo indispensabile elemento di un piano di gestione dei rifiuti che funzioni , non può essere colpa del governo centrale .
</s>
<s id="151:9" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=151&start=01.54&end=02.08&collection=eptic3">
Se il governo italiano ha dovuto mandare l' esercito - è successo qualche settimana fa ma altre volte in precedenza - per sostituire centinaia di netturbini improvvisamente e contemporaneamente ammalati , evidentemente non può essere colpa del governo centrale .
</s>
<s id="151:10" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=151&start=02.09&end=02.41&collection=eptic3">
Se l' emergenza ha colpito Napoli mentre nel resto dell' Italia le cose vanno assai diversamente , per esempio nella mia regione , il Veneto , dove la raccolta differenziata si fa da anni senza problemi e con tasso di riciclo altissimo , significa che le responsabilità dell' emergenza ricadono sulla politica campana e sugli amministratori locali e , soprattutto , sulle pesanti connivenze con la malavita che da sempre cerca e ottiene profitti grandissimi dal business dei rifiuti grazie all' infiltrazione della camorra nella politica e nelle amministrazioni locali .
</s>
</interpreter>
</st>
</speaker>
</text>
<text id="1854" date="2011-01-18" length="medium" lengthw="477" duration="medium" durations="211.0" speed="medium" speedwm="135.6" delivery="mixed" topic="Environment" topicspec="Waste crisis in Campania" type="Italian spoken sources" comments="NA">
<speaker name="Mazzoni Erminia" gender="F" country="Italy" politfunc="MEP" politgroup="PPE">
<st language="it" length="medium" lengthw="462" duration="medium" durations="213.0" speed="medium" speedwm="130.1" delivery="mixed">
<interpreter id="NA" gender="NA" native="NA">
<s id="1854:1" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=1854&start=00.06&end=00.30&collection=eptic3">
Grazie Presidente , io ringrazio il Commissario per aver voluto ricordare che la commissione petizioni ha dato un ruolo attivo a questo Parlamento , questo a dimostrazione che chi vi parla , e la parte politica che rappresenta , hanno il pieno interesse a farsi carico responsabilmente di questa situazione , a rendere tutte le procedure trasparenti e a coinvolgere i cittadini in un dialogo che responsabilizzi tutti quanti .
</s>
<s id="1854:2" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=1854&start=00.30&end=00.47&collection=eptic3">
Ehm come è stato già detto , lPIPPERO l' esecutivo regionale che , ricordo , si è insediato solo a maggio di quest' anno , ha sviluppato nei mesi scorsi un serrato dialogo con la Commissione europea , dando avvio ad un percorso che possiamo sicuramente definire diverso rispetto agli anni precedenti .
</s>
<s id="1854:3" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=1854&start=00.47&end=00.59&collection=eptic3">
Niente , però , di miracolistico , solo la presa in carico di una situazione drammatica che si è consolidata nell' arco di 15 anni di azioni inconcludenti o di non azioni .
</s>
<s id="1854:4" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=1854&start=00.59&end=01.10&collection=eptic3">
L' Italia è stata condannata - lo ricordo - dalla Corte di giustizia nel marzo 2010 , ma per fatti accertati e congelati al 2007 .
</s>
<s id="1854:5" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=1854&start=01.10&end=01.28&collection=eptic3">
Da allora la situazione , possiamo dire , è cambiata , l' assessore ehm regionale è venuto già 3 volte ehm qui a Bruxelles e ha già realizzato buona parte del " crono-programma " che è stato illustrato nel corso di un' audizione a luglio davanti alla commissione petizioni .
</s>
<s id="1854:6" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=1854&start=01.28&end=01.45&collection=eptic3">
Ehm rapidamente faccio un elenco : ha approvato il piano dei rifiuti speciali , definito il piano dei rifiuti ehm dei rifiuti solidi urbani , il 31 12 è stato presentato ehm l' ennesimo piano con le correzioni richieste dalla Commissione , piano che verrà approvato entro il 30 aprile come già comunicato .
</s>
<s id="1854:7" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=1854&start=01.45&end=02.17&collection=eptic3">
Il piano è stato già parzialmente avviato : sono stati messi in funzione , è stato messo in funzione il termovalorizzatore di Acerra , sono state espletate le procedure di gara per quello di Salerno , pubblicati i bandi per quello di Napoli Est , sono stati messi a regime 182 isole ecologiche , 7 impianti di recupero , 9 di compostaggio , 4 di selezione multimateriale , 1 per il trattamento dei RAEE , 2 di gestione aerobica , 34 piattaforme convenzionate e 5 discariche che mi fa piacere che possano essere controllate dalla Commissione .
</s>
<s id="1854:8" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=1854&start=02.17&end=02.30&collection=eptic3">
È stata conclusa l' intesa con le 5 province per lo smaltimento dei rifiuti accumulati e ancora , stipulati accordi con 5 regioni per il temporaneo trasferimento dei rifiuti , in attesa dell' entrata a regime definitiva del piano .
</s>
<s id="1854:9" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=1854&start=02.31&end=02.37&collection=eptic3">
È stata chiusa la gestione straordinaria e sono state reperite parziali risorse all' interno del bilancio regionale .
</s>
<s id="1854:10" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=1854&start=02.37&end=02.58&collection=eptic3">
Come ha detto la signora Bucella nel corso della sua recente audizione in commissione ambiente , i tempi di adeguamento alla sentenza normalmente variano , oscillano tra i 12 e i 24 mesi e quindi siamo perfettamente nei termini , ma la Commissione può discrezionalmente valutare un ampliamento dei tempi , compatibili realisticamente con lo stato di avanzamento dei lavori .
</s>
<s id="1854:11" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=1854&start=02.58&end=03.08&collection=eptic3">
Credo che in questa tempistica ci siano già tutte le risposte che gli interroganti hanno chiesto , non ci sono i presupposti , come ha detto il Commissario , per l' irrogazione di nuove sanzioni pecuniarie .
</s>
<s id="1854:12" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=1854&start=03.08&end=03.20&collection=eptic3">
La commassPIPPERO Commissione è giustamente attenta e io spero che questo dibattito non sia un dibattito strumentale che ehm metta ancora contro le istituzioni e le parti politiche .
</s>
<s id="1854:13" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=1854&start=03.20&end=03.37&collection=eptic3">
Se questo è un dibattito serio per aiutare la regione Campania , per cercare di trovare una soluzione a un problema antico , allora sicuramente anche la risoluzione che si immagina di votare a febbraio potrà essere una risoluzione comune , altrimenti sarà l' ennesima perdita di tempo che creerà ulteriori danni .
</s>
</interpreter>
</st>
</speaker>
</text>
<text id="155" date="2011-01-18" length="short" lengthw="279" duration="medium" durations="148.0" speed="slow" speedwm="113.1" delivery="read" topic="Environment" topicspec="Waste crisis in Campania" type="Italian spoken sources" comments="NA">
<speaker name="Pirillo Mario" gender="M" country="Italy" politfunc="MEP" politgroup="SD">
<st language="it" length="short" lengthw="272" duration="medium" durations="148.0" speed="slow" speedwm="110.3" delivery="read">
<interpreter id="NA" gender="NA" native="NA">
<s id="155:1" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=155&start=00.05&end=00.21&collection=eptic3">
Ehm signor Presidente , onorevoli colleghi , la profonda crisi che da anni vive la gestione del ciclo dei rifiuti campano non fa che preoccupare soprattutto per le pesanti ricadute sulla qualità della vita delle popolazioni locali .
</s>
<s id="155:2" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=155&start=00.21&end=00.43&collection=eptic3">
Come istituzione europea abbiamo il dovere di intervenire affinché questa situazione non si protragga oltremodo , tenendo alta l' attenzione e la soglia di guardia nei confronti delle autorità locali , spronandoli senza esitazione affinché adottino provvedimenti credibili , che permettano alla Campania di uscire da questa gravosa emergenza .
</s>
<s id="155:3" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=155&start=00.44&end=00.50&collection=eptic3">
La verità è che si è parlato tanto dell' emergenza rifiuti , senza sapere come stanno le cose .
</s>
<s id="155:4" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=155&start=00.50&end=00.58&collection=eptic3">
La regione Campania si era impegnata a presentare un piano regionale entro il 2010 , ora rinviato a marzo 2011 .
</s>
<s id="155:5" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=155&start=00.58&end=01.11&collection=eptic3">
La situazione diventerà ingestibile di fronte ad ulteriori rinvii : aumentano i rischi per la salute dei cittadini e la criminalità organizzata continua a lucrare sulle emergenze .
</s>
<s id="155:6" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=155&start=01.11&end=01.21&collection=eptic3">
Il governo italiano con decreto legge 195 del 2009 dichiara chiusa l' emergenza , delegando alle province la gestione del ciclo rifiuti .
</s>
<s id="155:7" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=155&start=01.21&end=01.31&collection=eptic3">
Decisione che non condividiamo e di difficile attuazione in una provincia come Napoli , dove risiede il 52 per cento della popolazione campana .
</s>
<s id="155:8" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=155&start=01.31&end=01.39&collection=eptic3">
Occorre rimettere al centro i comuni , solo essi sono capaci di dare risposte mirate ed efficaci .
</s>
<s id="155:9" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=155&start=01.39&end=01.47&collection=eptic3">
Diversi sindaci campani hanno avviato con notevole sforzo ed apprezzabili risultati la raccolta differenziata .
</s>
<s id="155:10" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=155&start=01.47&end=01.52&collection=eptic3">
Ad essi vanno assegnate quelle risorse già trasferite alla regione .
</s>
<s id="155:11" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=155&start=01.52&end=02.02&collection=eptic3">
Ascoltare le amministrazPIPPERO gli le amministrazioni locali è quanto mai necessario : stanno in prima linea e hanno una visione reale e complessiva del proprio territorio .
</s>
<s id="155:12" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=155&start=02.02&end=02.06&collection=eptic3">
Sono loro che lanciano l' allarme " discariche piene " .
</s>
<s id="155:13" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=155&start=02.06&end=02.26&collection=eptic3">
Servono nei prossimi mesi nuove discariche e nuovi inceneritori , vanno individuati i relativi siti , anche a seguito dell' esclusione di Cava Vitiello e di Terzigno su richiesta del territorio e del nostro Parlamento , e scongiurare il rischio di una paralisi dell' intero sistema di raccolta di rifiuti urbani .
</s>
<s id="155:14" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=155&start=02.26&end=02.32&collection=eptic3">
Aspettiamo la risposta della Commissione rispetto al piano presentato dalla regione Campania .
</s>
<s id="155:15" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=155&start=02.32&end=02.33&collection=eptic3">
Grazie .
</s>
</interpreter>
</st>
</speaker>
</text>
<text id="156" date="2011-01-18" length="short" lengthw="255" duration="short" durations="117.0" speed="medium" speedwm="130.8" delivery="read" topic="Environment" topicspec="Waste crisis in Campania" type="Italian spoken sources" comments="NA">
<speaker name="Alfano Sonia" gender="F" country="Italy" politfunc="MEP" politgroup="ALDE">
<st language="it" length="short" lengthw="250" duration="short" durations="117.0" speed="slow" speedwm="128.2" delivery="read">
<interpreter id="NA" gender="NA" native="NA">
<s id="156:1" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=156&start=00.06&end=00.16&collection=eptic3">
Grazie , signor Commissario , nonostante la propaganda del governo italiano , presto smentito dalla Commissione , l' emergenza dei rifiuti in Campania è un problema strutturale tutt' altro che risolto .
</s>
<s id="156:2" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=156&start=00.16&end=00.25&collection=eptic3">
Al di là di elenchi discutibili , ehm bisogna rendersi conto di un unico dato di fatto : cioè i cittadini campani continuano a vivere , e a morire , in mezzo ai rifiuti .
</s>
<s id="156:3" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=156&start=00.26&end=00.32&collection=eptic3">
La classe politica locale , regionale e nazionale , a destra come a sinistra , ha pesantissime responsabilità .
</s>
<s id="156:4" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=156&start=00.32&end=00.40&collection=eptic3">
Adesso la soluzione del problema non può essere scaricata sui cittadini , già vittime di condaPIPPERO di condizioni di vita assolutamente insalubri .
</s>
<s id="156:5" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=156&start=00.40&end=00.46&collection=eptic3">
L' Unione europea deve imporre che la soluzione sia virtuosa , altrimenti il suo interesPIPPERO il suo intervento risulterebbe vano .
</s>
<s id="156:6" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=156&start=00.46&end=00.54&collection=eptic3">
Non è costruendo gli inceneritori , peraltro finanziati come fonti rinnovabili in contrasto alla normativa europea vigente , che si risolve la questione .
</s>
<s id="156:7" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=156&start=00.54&end=00.58&collection=eptic3">
I rifiuti verrebbero trasformati in ceneri , emissioni nocive e mortali .
</s>
<s id="156:8" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=156&start=00.59&end=01.12&collection=eptic3">
Gli inceneritori , ce lo dice la direttiva rifiuti , sono l' ultima opzione gerarchica di un ciclo integrato di rifiuti che presenta alternative virtuose senza impatto sulla salute dei cittadini e sull' ambiente e che , anzi , creano occupazione .
</s>
<s id="156:9" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=156&start=01.12&end=01.24&collection=eptic3">
E rispetto alle infiltrazioni mafiose , ehm ritengo sia opportuno prendere atto che le infiltrazioni mafiose , soprattutto nel campo dei rifiuti , sono al Sud ma soprattutto al Nord , specialmente negli ultimi anni .
</s>
<s id="156:10" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=156&start=01.24&end=01.39&collection=eptic3">
Pongo pertanto alla Commissione 3 domande : come intende agire per evitare che la soluzione del problema ricada sulla salute dei cittadini e che cosa intende fare per evitare che ai cittadini vengano imposte decisioni e che vengano addirittura militarizzati i territori ?
</s>
<s id="156:11" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=156&start=01.39&end=01.47&collection=eptic3">
Ritiene opportuno porre tra le condizioni per la chiusura della procedura di infrazione l' immediata attivazione del registro tumori per l' intera regione ?
</s>
<s id="156:12" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=156&start=01.48&end=02.02&collection=eptic3">
In che maniera la Commissione valuta la legge 210 del 2008 e , in particolare , l' articolo 9 relativo agli incentivi per la realizzazione degli inceneritori , nel quale viene violata palesemente la normativa comunitaria relativa agli aiuti di Stato ?
</s>
<s id="156:13" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=156&start=02.02&end=02.03&collection=eptic3">
Grazie .
</s>
</interpreter>
</st>
</speaker>
</text>
<text id="158" date="2011-01-18" length="short" lengthw="170" duration="short" durations="68.0" speed="medium" speedwm="150.0" delivery="mixed" topic="Environment" topicspec="Waste crisis in Campania" type="Italian spoken sources" comments="NA">
<speaker name="Rossi Oreste" gender="M" country="Italy" politfunc="MEP" politgroup="EFD">
<st language="it" length="short" lengthw="172" duration="short" durations="68.0" speed="medium" speedwm="151.8" delivery="mixed">
<interpreter id="NA" gender="NA" native="NA">
<s id="158:1" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=158&start=00.04&end=00.13&collection=eptic3">
# Presidente , il piano di smaltimento rifiuti è predisposto , deve essere attuato prevedendo la raccolta differenziata , riciclo e , solo per la parte finale , incenerimento .
</s>
<s id="158:2" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=158&start=00.13&end=00.27&collection=eptic3">
Pensare di infliggere nuove sanzioni non sarebbe corretto e , guardi , le ricordo che la colpa non è né del Nord , né di altre forze politiche , il sua il gruppo a cui lei appartiene dei Verdi aveva persino il ministro prima , quindi attenzione .
</s>
<s id="158:3" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=158&start=00.27&end=00.37&collection=eptic3">
Dell' emergenza rifiuti a Napoli e nella regione Campania sono decenni che se ne parla e , nonostante sian stati stanziati copiosi fondi , è vero , ad oggi si è ancora in situazione di emergenza , ma non ci sono scuse .
</s>
<s id="158:4" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=158&start=00.38&end=00.49&collection=eptic3">
Dire che la responsabilità è del Nord dell' Italia , e addirittura che adesso vi sarebbero - diceva la collega - i rifiuti del Nord per le strade di Napoli , beh , sono semplicemente falsità .
</s>
<s id="158:5" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=158&start=00.49&end=01.03&collection=eptic3">
Perché , la responsabilità palese è delle precedenti amministrazioni locali che , mentre da una parte hanno consentito alla malavita organizzata di fare liberamente traffici illeciti di rifiuti , dall' altra non hanno saputo predisporre idonee ed adeguate aree di raccolta e smaltimento .
</s>
<s id="158:6" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=158&start=01.03&end=01.13&collection=eptic3">
Quello che è necessario è che i cittadini campani e napoletani abbiano il coraggio , con il loro voto , come è già successo a livello regionale , di sostituire gli amministratori incapaci .
</s>
</interpreter>
</st>
</speaker>
</text>
<text id="159" date="2011-01-18" length="short" lengthw="231" duration="short" durations="114.0" speed="slow" speedwm="121.6" delivery="read" topic="Environment" topicspec="Waste crisis in Campania" type="Italian spoken sources" comments="NA">
<speaker name="Rivellini Crescenzio" gender="M" country="Italy" politfunc="MEP" politgroup="PPE">
<st language="it" length="short" lengthw="230" duration="short" durations="114.0" speed="slow" speedwm="121.1" delivery="read">
<interpreter id="NA" gender="NA" native="NA">
<s id="159:1" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=159&start=00.05&end=00.18&collection=eptic3">
Grazie Presidente , e ringrazio l' onorevole Seeber e tutti i miei colleghi per il compito assegnatomi , ma permettetemi di sottolineare che già sono in corso in Campania azioni estremamente positive .
</s>
<s id="159:2" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=159&start=00.19&end=00.28&collection=eptic3">
Ritengo pertanto che il ricorso all' articolo ex 260 del regolamento da parte di alcuni per ottenere sanzioni pecuniarie siano strumentali .
</s>
<s id="159:3" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=159&start=00.29&end=00.38&collection=eptic3">
La giunta regionale , insediatasi solo da pochi mesi , ha già pronto il piano relativo ai rifiuti speciali e il piano sul ciclo integrato dei rifiuti .
</s>
<s id="159:4" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=159&start=00.38&end=00.48&collection=eptic3">
Inoltre , è iniziata una politica relativa alla raccolta differenziate e sono state avviate iniziative per ridurre complessivamente i rifiuti prodotti .
</s>
<s id="159:5" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=159&start=00.48&end=00.58&collection=eptic3">
È in corso a Salerno la gara per la realizzazione di un inceneritore e sono in fase avanzata le procedure per la pubblicazione del bando per l' inceneritore a Napoli Est .
</s>
<s id="159:6" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=159&start=00.58&end=01.17&collection=eptic3">
Finalmente , le politiche attuate hanno lo scopo non solo di pulire la città , ma di organizzare un ciclo integrato di rifiuti con la raccolta differenziata , la diminuzione dei rifiuti prodotti , la realizzazione di impianti moderni anche per eliminare le ecoballe e la bonifica delle vecchie discariche .
</s>
<s id="159:7" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=159&start=01.18&end=01.37&collection=eptic3">
Per ciò che è accaduto in passato si puniscano i veri responsabili , che sono certo tra gli ex amministratori campani di sinistra e , in particolare , dei Verdi , ma anche alcuni che dal Nord Italia hanno sfruttato la malavita locale per scaricare i rifiuti tossici che hanno prodotto .
</s>
<s id="159:8" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=159&start=01.37&end=01.51&collection=eptic3">
La Comunità europea deve aiutare la Campania , senza pregiudizi , e mi appello a tutti affinché si lavori per , e non contro , solo per soddisfare mediaticamente il proprio partito o la propria ideologia .
</s>
<s id="159:9" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=159&start=01.52&end=01.58&collection=eptic3">
Ma veramente pensate... che penalizzando pecuniariamente la Campania si risolve l' emergenza ?
</s>
</interpreter>
</st>
</speaker>
</text>
<text id="161" date="2011-01-18" length="short" lengthw="153" duration="short" durations="74.0" speed="slow" speedwm="124.1" delivery="impromptu" topic="Environment" topicspec="Waste crisis in Campania" type="Italian spoken sources" comments="NA">
<speaker name="De Magistris Luigi" gender="M" country="Italy" politfunc="MEP" politgroup="ALDE">
<st language="it" length="short" lengthw="155" duration="short" durations="74.0" speed="slow" speedwm="125.7" delivery="impromptu">
<interpreter id="NA" gender="NA" native="NA">
<s id="161:1" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=161&start=00.05&end=00.29&collection=eptic3">
Sì , dopo le bugie del governo Berlusconi che si è insediato nel 2008 dicendo agli italiani che il problema dei rifiuti era superato , fa bene l' Unione europea a bloccare i fondi all' Italia fino a quando non verrà presentato un ciclo dei rifiuti ecocompatibile , che si fondi sul... riciclaggio dei rifiuti e sul compostaggio .
</s>
<s id="161:2" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=161&start=00.29&end=00.47&collection=eptic3">
E non è certo il piano che ha presentato il Presidente Caldoro , che si fonda ancora una volta su discariche incontrollate come quella di Chiaiano , di Taverna del Re , di Terzigno , addirittura nel Parco nazionale del Vesuvio , né degli inceneritori che producono morte , tumori e una vera e propria emergenza sanitaria .
</s>
<s id="161:3" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=161&start=00.47&end=01.01&collection=eptic3">
I soldi pubblici in Campania nell' emergenza ambientale di questi 13 anni hanno consolidato i rapporti criminali tra la politica , tanto di sinistra quanto di destra , degli imprenditori e della camorra .
</s>
<s id="161:4" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=161&start=01.01&end=01.18&collection=eptic3">
E né le questioni ambientali si risolvono con la criminalizzazione del dissenso , con le criminalizzazioni delle comunità locali , delle famiglie e del territorio , come ha fatto il governo italiano utilizzando il manganello per reprimere chi difende la natura e il territorio .
</s>
</interpreter>
</st>
</speaker>
</text>
<text id="168" date="2011-01-18" length="long" lengthw="65" duration="short" durations="54.0" speed="slow" speedwm="72.2" delivery="mixed" topic="Environment" topicspec="Waste crisis in Campania" type="Italian spoken sources" comments="NA">
<speaker name="Speroni Francesco Enrico" gender="M" country="Italy" politfunc="MEP" politgroup="EFD">
<st language="it" length="long" lengthw="67" duration="short" durations="54.0" speed="slow" speedwm="74.4" delivery="mixed">
<interpreter id="NA" gender="NA" native="NA">
<s id="168:1" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=168&start=00.05&end=00.19&collection=eptic3">
Grazie Presidente , l' Europa , centralista e burocratica , non distingue le differenze territoriali e le articolazioni amministrative all' interno degli Stati membri .
</s>
<s id="168:2" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=168&start=00.19&end=00.51&collection=eptic3">
Le responsabilità della disastrosa situazione in Campania è... principalmente dei cittadini campani e io , da padano , respingo queste accuse e le ribalto contro quelli che in Campania hanno votato amministratori locali incapaci di risolvere il problema e hanno persistito nell' errore confermandoli in successive tornate elettorali .
</s>
<s id="168:3" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=168&start=00.51&end=00.58&collection=eptic3">
La Padania è disponibile ad aiutare i campani , ma non accetta le accuse .
</s>
</interpreter>
</st>
</speaker>
</text>
<text id="163" date="2011-01-18" length="short" lengthw="233" duration="medium" durations="142.0" speed="slow" speedwm="98.5" delivery="read" topic="Environment" topicspec="Waste crisis in Campania" type="Italian spoken sources" comments="NA">
<speaker name="Baldassarre Raffaele" gender="M" country="Italy" politfunc="MEP" politgroup="PPE">
<st language="it" length="short" lengthw="231" duration="medium" durations="142.0" speed="slow" speedwm="97.6" delivery="read">
<interpreter id="NA" gender="NA" native="NA">
<s id="163:1" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=163&start=00.04&end=00.28&collection=eptic3">
Grazie Presidente , egregio Commissario , colleghe e colleghi , non voglio certo con il mio intervento negare la gravità di una situazione che è la conseguenza inevitabile di una palese insufficienza amministrativa e politica che ha rischiato , e rischia ancora , di soffocare un' intera città e il suo circondario di rifiuti .
</s>
<s id="163:2" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=163&start=00.28&end=01.00&collection=eptic3">
Onorevole Søndergaard e onorevole Lichtenberger , l' emergenza in Campania è nata e si è così drammaticamente sviluppata per l' incapacità di una giunta regionale e di un' amministrazione comunale di Napoli , di sinistra e con assessori Verdi , di compiere scelte , anche impopolari e coraggiose , per realizzare il ciclo virtuoso della raccolta e lo smaltimento dell' immondizia .
</s>
<s id="163:3" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=163&start=01.01&end=01.16&collection=eptic3">
Irresponsabilità , indecisioni , convenienze politiche , connivenze oscure , sprechi hanno caratterizzato una fase politica e amministrativa che oggi si è definitivamente chiusa .
</s>
<s id="163:4" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=163&start=01.17&end=01.26&collection=eptic3">
Voglio rassicurare i firmatari delle interrogazioni ed i gruppi politici che li hanno appoggiate che la situazione politica ed operativa è completamente cambiata .
</s>
<s id="163:5" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=163&start=01.26&end=01.45&collection=eptic3">
Il governo nazionale e la nuova giunta regionale , in modo responsabile , hanno la determinazione politica di risolvere l' emergenza , superando con il confronto con le popolazioni interessate sia con la doverosa risolutezza ostacoli e resistenti che spesso nascono dalla sindrome di Nimby :
</s>
<s id="163:6" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=163&start=01.45&end=01.49&collection=eptic3">
" Non voglio la tua spazzatura nel mio giardino " .
</s>
<s id="163:7" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=163&start=01.49&end=02.01&collection=eptic3">
A tale fine , hanno predisposto un piano integrato di raccolta e smaltimento rifiuti che prevede in tempi brevi l' incentivazione alla raccolta differenziata e la realizzazione degli impianti necessari .
</s>
<s id="163:8" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=163&start=02.01&end=02.28&collection=eptic3">
Sarebbe pertanto estremamente ingiusto , controproducente e strumentale , così come chiede l' onorevole de Magistris , imporre oggi sanzioni e provvedimenti inibitori che colpirebbero istituzioni che , attraverso l' efficiente utilizzo delle risorse comunitarie e nazionali stanno cercando , in piena collaborazione con l' Unione europea , di chiudere definitivamente questa brutta pagina della millenaria storia di Napoli e della Campania .
</s>
</interpreter>
</st>
</speaker>
</text>
<text id="169" date="2011-01-18" length="short" lengthw="219" duration="short" durations="107.0" speed="slow" speedwm="122.8" delivery="read" topic="Environment" topicspec="Waste crisis in Campania" type="Italian spoken sources" comments="NA">
<speaker name="Comi Lara" gender="F" country="Italy" politfunc="MEP" politgroup="PPE">
<st language="it" length="short" lengthw="220" duration="short" durations="107.0" speed="slow" speedwm="123.4" delivery="read">
<interpreter id="NA" gender="NA" native="NA">
<s id="169:1" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=169&start=00.05&end=00.18&collection=eptic3">
Caro Commissario , cari colleghi , grazie Presidente , con il mio intervento voglio affermare in modo chiaro che la situazione dei rifiuti in Campania è migliorata rispetto al passato ed è in corso di definizione .
</s>
<s id="169:2" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=169&start=00.19&end=00.27&collection=eptic3">
La problematica è molto complessa , presenta difficoltà di vario genere e necessità di tempo per essere risolta in modo adeguato e definitivo .
</s>
<s id="169:3" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=169&start=00.27&end=00.40&collection=eptic3">
Le interrogazioni orali sulle quali discutiamo invocano l' applicazione della procedura ai sensi dell' articolo 260 del trattato , ma non è l' applicazione di una sanzione pecuniaria che risolverà la situazione in Campania .
</s>
<s id="169:4" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=169&start=00.41&end=00.57&collection=eptic3">
Così procedendo , rischieremmo di avvallare un criterio di attribuzione della responsabilità per infrazione a uno Stato membro sul piano meramente oggettivo , semplicemente per non aver ancora adempiuto oggettivamente un obbligo derivante dall' ordinamento comunitario .
</s>
<s id="169:5" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=169&start=00.57&end=01.02&collection=eptic3">
Ciò che deve esser preso in considerazione è anche il comportamento soggettivo dello Stato .
</s>
<s id="169:6" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=169&start=01.03&end=01.20&collection=eptic3">
Non si può certo dire che l' Italia non abbia rispettato l' obbligo di leale cooperazione , ma come il signor Commissario ha confermato , i servizi della Commissione sono in continuo contatto con le autorità italiane nazionali e territoriali e seguono scrupolosamente l' evolversi della situazione .
</s>
<s id="169:7" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=169&start=01.20&end=01.25&collection=eptic3">
La volontà e l' impegno profusi dall' Italia sono assolutamente innegabili .
</s>
<s id="169:8" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=169&start=01.26&end=01.35&collection=eptic3">
È importante sottolineare che il ruolo operativo è passato dalle regioni alle province , in modo tale da sviluppare un piano idoneo alle diverse esigenze del territorio .
</s>
<s id="169:9" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=169&start=01.35&end=01.39&collection=eptic3">
L' Europa deve essere vicina all' Italia , cooperando in perfetta sinergia .
</s>
<s id="169:10" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=169&start=01.39&end=01.52&collection=eptic3">
Vorrei concludere ricordando che nella giunta regionale campana era presente anche l' Italia dei Valori , che forse ora ha la memoria corta e troppo corta per ricordare quello che ha fatto o che , meglio , non ha fatto .
</s>
</interpreter>
</st>
</speaker>
</text>
<text id="173" date="2011-01-18" length="short" lengthw="258" duration="medium" durations="137.0" speed="slow" speedwm="113.0" delivery="read" topic="Environment" topicspec="Waste crisis in Campania" type="Italian spoken sources" comments="NA">
<speaker name="Matera Barbara" gender="F" country="Italy" politfunc="MEP" politgroup="PPE">
<st language="it" length="short" lengthw="257" duration="medium" durations="137.0" speed="slow" speedwm="112.6" delivery="read">
<interpreter id="NA" gender="NA" native="NA">
<s id="173:1" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=173&start=00.05&end=00.20&collection=eptic3">
Grazie Presidente , non intervengo per mero campanilismo , ma per condividere con voi la risposta italiana alla violazione comunitaria , ricordando che è nostro interesse difendere gli interessi dei cittadini e del nostro popolo .
</s>
<s id="173:2" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=173&start=00.20&end=00.32&collection=eptic3">
La regione Campania e , in generale , lo Stato italiano stanno provvedendo alla creazione di una rete di impianti di smaltimento dei rifiuti secondo quanto stabilito dal diritto comunitario .
</s>
<s id="173:3" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=173&start=00.32&end=00.48&collection=eptic3">
Voglio ricordare che l' utilizzo dei fondi comunitari stanziati per lo smaltimento di rifiuti in Campania sono stati impiegati nei POR 2000 - 2006 nella misura 1.7 e nei POR 2007 - 2013 , obiettivo operativo 1.1 .
</s>
<s id="173:4" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=173&start=00.49&end=01.20&collection=eptic3">
Sul POR 2000 - 2006 la regione Campania ha rendicontato la dotazione finanziaria disponibile pari a 140 milioni di euro , soldi impegnati nella realizzazione di : impianti di stoccaggio , trattamento e recupero , impianti di valorizzazione , frazione umida e secca e la messa in sicurezza di discariche per costruzione , o ampliamento , di impianti destinati al recupero di materia da rifiuti , per interventi a sostegno della raccolta differenziata .
</s>
<s id="173:5" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=173&start=01.20&end=01.38&collection=eptic3">
Per quanto attiene al POR 2007 - 2013 , sono stati stanziati 110 milioni di euro per la realizzazione di impianti per il trattamento di rifiuti , 50 milioni di euro per il finanziamento di impianti comunali per la raccolta differenziata .
</s>
<s id="173:6" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=173&start=01.38&end=02.08&collection=eptic3">
