</s>
<s id="186:6" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=186&start=01.13&end=01.20&collection=eptic3">
In questa direzione c ' è un grande lavoro da fare da parte dell' Europa , sia sul piano politico , diplomatico che culturale e sociale .
</s>
<s id="186:7" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=186&start=01.20&end=01.32&collection=eptic3">
Oggi chiediamo con forza al Consiglio e alla Commissione , soprattutto all' alto rappresentante per la politica estera , di adottare chiare linee guida nella relazione con i paesi terzi nell' ambito del nuovo servizio esterno .
</s>
<s id="186:8" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=186&start=01.32&end=01.43&collection=eptic3">
Anche gli accordi bilaterali debbono porre maggiore attenzione ai temi della libertà religiosa e , più in generale , ai diritti umani , il cui mancato rispetto sia motivo di messa in mora di questi accordi .
</s>
<s id="186:9" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=186&start=01.43&end=01.57&collection=eptic3">
Penso , tra l' altro , all' avvio di un protagonismo europeo sul dialogo interreligioso , la cui assenza spesso supera i singoli incidenti e prende la strada di veri e proprie guerre dove la religione copre ragioni più complesse dei conflitti .
</s>
<s id="186:10" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=186&start=01.57&end=02.02&collection=eptic3">
Dobbiamo infine guardare anche in casa nostra : in Europa non mancano episodi di intolleranza .
</s>
<s id="186:11" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=186&start=02.03&end=02.15&collection=eptic3">
Le nostre città vivono la condizione oggettiva di multiculuPIPPERO ehm culturalità che porta con sé tradizioni e valori religiosi che devono essere rispettati ed ai quali va garantita la libertà di espressione .
</s>
<s id="186:12" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=186&start=02.15&end=02.18&collection=eptic3">
Non c ' è alternativa , dunque , al dialogo e al rispetto reciproco .
</s>
<s id="186:13" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=186&start=02.18&end=02.23&collection=eptic3">
È importante ribadire l' appello delle comunità religiose e del loro...
</s>
</interpreter>
</st>
</speaker>
</text>
<text id="187" date="2011-01-19" length="short" lengthw="218" duration="short" durations="93.0" speed="medium" speedwm="140.6" delivery="read" topic="Society and Culture" topicspec="Situation of Christians in the context of freedom of religion" type="Italian spoken sources" comments="NA">
