<text id="2386" date="2011-02-15" length="short" lengthw="198" duration="medium" durations="129.0" speed="slow" speedwm="92.1" delivery="impromptu" topic="Politics" topicspec="Immediate EU measures in support of Italy and other Member States affected by exceptional migration flows" type="Italian spoken sources" comments="NA">
<speaker name="Mauro Mario" gender="M" country="Italy" politfunc="MEP" politgroup="PPE">
<st language="it" length="short" lengthw="195" duration="medium" durations="129.0" speed="slow" speedwm="90.7" delivery="impromptu">
<interpreter id="NA" gender="NA" native="NA">
<s id="2386:1" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=2386&start=00.00&end=00.21&collection=eptic3">
Grazie signor Presidente ehm, signora Commissario innanzitutto la ringrazio per ehm l'impegno che sta profondendo e che ancor più vorrà profondere per far fronte a questa emergenza, una emergenza umanitaria.
</s>
<s id="2386:2" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=2386&start=00.21&end=00.40&collection=eptic3">
Lei però sa bene quanto me, che la vera emergenza non è quella umanitaria, quella umanitaria è un effetto, ma la vera emergenza è il fatto che, nel sommovimento epocale che sta riguardando l'intera area del Maghreb, l'Europa appare...
</s>
<s id="2386:3" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=2386&start=00.40&end=00.50&collection=eptic3">
inadeguata, incapace cioè di rifondare una strategia per il Mediterraneo che più volte ha tentato e che è sempre fallita.
</s>
<s id="2386:4" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=2386&start=00.50&end=00.54&collection=eptic3">
È fallito il processo di Lisbona, è fallita miseramente l'Unione per il Mediterraneo.
</s>
<s id="2386:5" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=2386&start=00.54&end=01.03&collection=eptic3">
Non abbiamo una visione adeguata di quelli che sono i problemi sul tappeto: abbiamo necessità di affrontarli insieme, e oggi il Consiglio non c'è.
</s>
<s id="2386:6" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=2386&start=01.03&end=01.18&collection=eptic3">
Abbiamo chiesto che il Consiglio si ponga il problema di avere una strategia europea per il problema, non tanto dell'immigrazione e dell'immigrazione clandestina, ma per il problema della democrazia e della libertà in tutta l'area del Mediterraneo.
</s>
<s id="2386:7" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=2386&start=01.18&end=01.35&collection=eptic3">
Quando è caduto il blocco sovietico, tutti insieme, facendo fronte comune, abbiamo dato risposte concrete, e abbiamo saltato a piè pari il problema delle migliaia di polacchi presenti nelle nostre piazze perché ci siamo posti il problema dell'integrazione europea di tutto l'Est.
</s>
<s id="2386:8" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=2386&start=01.35&end=01.38&collection=eptic3">
Ora, rispetto al Mediterraneo, tacciamo.
</s>
<s id="2386:9" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=2386&start=01.38&end=02.00&collection=eptic3">
E invece dobbiamo avere una strategia, senza quella strategia ci mancherà la possibilità di dare risposte.
</s>
<s id="2386:10" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=2386&start=02.00&end=02.09&collection=eptic3">
Apprezzeremo la sua buona volontà e ci fermeremo lì.
</s>
<s id="2386:11" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=2386&start=02.09&end=02.09&collection=eptic3">
Grazie.
</s>
</interpreter>
</st>
</speaker>
</text>
<text id="2390" date="2011-02-15" length="short" lengthw="185" duration="short" durations="118.0" speed="slow" speedwm="94.1" delivery="impromptu" topic="Politics" topicspec="Immediate EU measures in support of Italy and other Member States affected by exceptional migration flows" type="Italian spoken sources" comments="NA">
