</s>
<s id="2394:5" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=2394&start=00.49&end=01.38&collection=eptic3">
Noi dobbiamo avere con chiPIPPERO ehm con chiaro che in questo momento non è in discussione il problem-, come diceva Vidar, il problema di Frontex o come ehm o come bloccare i gli sbarchi, perché noi ci troviamo di fronte ai popolPIPPERO a popoli che abbiamo sollecitato che loPIPPERO lottassero per la democrazia, lo fanno, ora dobbiamo avere la capacità di accoglierli  e allargare i visti è una delle politiche che può fare l’Italia per cercare di aiutare questi paesi.
</s>
</interpreter>
</st>
</speaker>
</text>
<text id="2398" date="2011-02-15" length="short" lengthw="164" duration="short" durations="105.0" speed="slow" speedwm="93.7" delivery="impromptu" topic="Justice" topicspec="Eavesdropping scandal in Bulgaria" type="Italian spoken sources" comments="NA">
<speaker name="Rinaldi Niccolò" gender="M" country="Italy" politfunc="MEP" politgroup="ALDE">
<st language="it" length="short" lengthw="140" duration="short" durations="105.0" speed="slow" speedwm="80.0" delivery="impromptu">
<interpreter id="NA" gender="NA" native="NA">
<s id="2398:1" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=2398&start=00.00&end=00.12&collection=eptic3">
Grazie signor Presidente, io sono un liberaldemocratico ehm sia in Europa, che in Italia.
</s>
<s id="2398:2" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=2398&start=00.12&end=00.25&collection=eptic3">
A volte nel mio paese, insieme ai compagni del mio partito, capita di essere definiti comunisti, comunisti soltanto perché siamo opposizione al governo ehm che è attualmente in carica.
</s>
<s id="2398:3" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=2398&start=00.25&end=00.27&collection=eptic3">
E, da quello che...
</s>
<s id="2398:4" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=2398&start=00.27&end=00.41&collection=eptic3">
possiamo leggere, da quello che ci risulta, una cosa del genere sta accadendo ai miei colleghi bulgari – liberaldemocratici o socialisti – che vengono definiti criminali soltanto perché sono forza di opposizione nel loro paese.
</s>
<s id="2398:5" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=2398&start=00.41&end=00.55&collection=eptic3">
È una deriva che non ci piace perché ehm fino a un certo punto si può anche scherzare di queste cose, ma naturalmente può ehm assumere, ehm è un comportamento che può assumere degli aspetti alla fine anche molto molto pericolosi.
</s>
<s id="2398:6" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=2398&start=00.55&end=01.14&collection=eptic3">
Del resto, il mio ministro degli Esteri non più tardi di ieri – dopo tutto quello che è successo in Egitto e Tunisia – è andato a Damasco, in Siria, e ha definito la Siria 'un paese democratico che soddisfa pienamente il bisogno di modernizzazione dei propri cittadini'.
</s>
<s id="2398:7" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=2398&start=01.14&end=01.45&collection=eptic3">
Se questo è il discorso dei nostri rappresentanti, noi come parlamentari europei dobbiamo denunciarlo, ma voi, come Commissione, assolutamente dovete vigilare.
</s>
</interpreter>
</st>
</speaker>
</text>
<text id="2402" date="2011-02-16" length="short" lengthw="251" duration="medium" durations="149.0" speed="slow" speedwm="101.1" delivery="impromptu" topic="Politics" topicspec="Media law in Hungary" type="Italian spoken sources" comments="NA">
<speaker name="Scurria Marco" gender="M" country="Italy" politfunc="MEP" politgroup="PPE">
<st language="it" length="short" lengthw="216" duration="medium" durations="149.0" speed="slow" speedwm="87.0" delivery="impromptu">
<interpreter id="NA" gender="NA" native="NA">
<s id="2402:1" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=2402&start=00.00&end=01.02&collection=eptic3">
#ehm grazie, ma ehm intervengo in questo dibattito in maniera un po' imbarazzata, perché il ehm la Commissaria ci ha praticamente detto che è inutile che facciamo questo dibattito, perché non c'è la ragione del contendere, perché, come probabilmente, se ci avessero anche ascoltato gli altri nostri colleghi, avevamo già detto nelle occasioni precedenti e cioè durante le commissioni, durante quest'Aula, forse bisognava essere, aspettare un po', perché in fin dei conti il governo ungherese si era sempre dimostrato disponibile a venire incontro a quelle che erano le osservazioni che sarebbero appunto arrivate dalla Commissione europea – sembrava strano il contrario # in quel momento rappresenta ricopre la carica della Presidenza della nostra Unione, chiaramente non seguire le indicazioni che venivano dalla Commissione europea.
</s>
<s id="2402:2" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=2402&start=01.02&end=01.20&collection=eptic3">
Però si è voluto andare avanti ugualmente, forse – anzi, sicuramente – c’era più di qualche elemento ideologico, c’era sicuramente qualche elemento politico, per cui questo dibattito si doveva tenere e se sonPIPPERO e sono state presentate le risoluzioni di cui tra l'altro domani si dovrebbe ehm votare.
</s>
<s id="2402:3" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=2402&start=01.20&end=01.40&collection=eptic3">
Probabilmente bisognava avere più accortezza, probabilmente bisognava avere più fiducia nei governi eletti democraticamente dai popoli, a cominciare da quello ungherese, eletto abbondantemente dal proprio popolo, talmente con una percentuale talmente vasta che non ha certo bisogno di manipolare i media per avere il proprio consenso nel proprio paese.
</s>
<s id="2402:4" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=2402&start=01.40&end=02.23&collection=eptic3">
Per cui, io penso che ehm la cosa più utile che si possa fare è invitare i nostri colleghi socialisti e liberali, che hanno presentato le risoluzioni di un certo tipo, di sospendere questa ipotesi, di evitare di coprirsi di ridicolo, di ritirare le proprie risoluzioni e lasciare questo Parlamento al lavoro di cose reali di cui i cittadini europei hanno bisogno.
</s>
<s id="2402:5" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=2402&start=02.23&end=02.29&collection=eptic3">
E ringrazio ovviamente la Commissaria per il suo lavoro.
</s>
</interpreter>
</st>
</speaker>
</text>
<text id="2406" date="2011-02-16" length="short" lengthw="129" duration="short" durations="85.0" speed="slow" speedwm="91.1" delivery="impromptu" topic="Politics" topicspec="Media law in Hungary" type="Italian spoken sources" comments="NA">
<speaker name="Mauro Mario" gender="M" country="Italy" politfunc="MEP" politgroup="PPE">
<st language="it" length="short" lengthw="124" duration="short" durations="85.0" speed="slow" speedwm="87.5" delivery="impromptu">
<interpreter id="NA" gender="NA" native="NA">
<s id="2406:1" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=2406&start=00.00&end=00.26&collection=eptic3">
Grazie Presidente, ehm, anche volendo credere che chi ha criticato così fortemente ehm la legge ungherese voglia effettivamente solo ed esclusivamente la libertà per i media, io credo però che dobbiamo avere rispetto per il lavoro fatto dalla Commissione e per i contenuti espressi dal dibattito in Parlamento.
</s>
<s id="2406:2" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=2406&start=00.26&end=00.44&collection=eptic3">
Credo cioè che dobbiamo assumerci la responsabilità – per evitare una brutta pagina nella storia del nostro Parlamento – di non votare domani, semplicemente di annullare una risoluzione perché si basa su contenuti che non corrispondono a realtà, come ha dimostrato l'intervento del Commissario.
</s>
<s id="2406:3" video="https://media.dipintra.it/?id=2406&start=00.44&end=01.25&collection=eptic3">
Allora io invito anche il Consiglio e la Commissione, in modo informale, a prendere anche contatto con la Conferenza dei Presidenti, perché ci sia quello scambio, necessario e indispensabile, di informazioni che permetta domani all'Aula di votare, prima ancora delle risoluzioni, la decisione di non votarle più e di porre fine a dibattiti di contenuto ideologico.
</s>
</interpreter>
</st>
</speaker>
</text>